20 REM *** Z=LEFT X=RIGHT /=THRUST SPC=FIRE ***
30 GOSUB 5000: REM INIT
40 GOSUB 6000: REM MAIN GAME LOOP
50 END

100 REM ========================
110 REM === CONSTANTS / DATA ===
120 REM ========================
130 REM SCREEN: 128x48 PIXELS
140 REM SHIP DIRECTIONS: 1-8 (1=UP, clockwise)
150 REM DIR 1=UP 2=UR 3=RT 4=DR 5=DN 6=DL 7=LT 8=UL

500 REM ========================
510 REM === INIT SUBROUTINE  ===
520 REM ========================

600 REM ========================
610 REM === SPAWN ASTEROIDS  ===
620 REM ========================

800 REM ========================
810 REM === MAIN GAME LOOP   ===
820 REM ========================

900 REM ========================
910 REM === DRAW SHIP        ===
920 REM ========================

1000 REM ========================
1010 REM === INPUT HANDLER    ===
1020 REM ========================

1100 REM ========================
1110 REM === MOVE SHIP        ===
1120 REM ========================

1200 REM ========================
1210 REM === MOVE BULLETS     ===
1220 REM ========================

1300 REM ========================
1310 REM === MOVE ASTEROIDS   ===
1320 REM ========================

1400 REM ========================
1410 REM === COLLISION CHECK  ===
1420 REM ========================

